    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>El Psy Congroo ╮(╯▽╰)╭</p><span id="more"></span><p> &amp;nbsp&amp;nbsp 空格 nbsp$~~~~~$.</p><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">JustTestCSStyle</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Console.WriteLine(<span class="number">233</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Todo:<br>学习做个字母动画<br>字体<br>local search<br>RSS<br>md渲染器   比如代码渲染,空格渲染<br>### Pandoc</p><h3 id="打字特效">打字特效</h3><p>next/layout/<em>custom/cutom.njk/</em></p><h3 id="文章置顶">文章置顶</h3><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm uni hexo-generator-index</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-index-pin-top --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>提供更好的 Markdown 渲染，主要有两点好处：脚注、MathJax。详情参考</p>        <div id="aplayer-ufXmOWDp" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">            <pre class="aplayer-lrc-content"></pre>        </div>        <script>          var ap = new APlayer({            element: document.getElementById("aplayer-ufXmOWDp"),            narrow: false,            autoplay: false,            showlrc: false,            music: {              title: "title",              author: "author",              url: "https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1u7dE6gzMjclBb0_B2uln50AMIdVEIuVe",              pic: "",              lrc: ""            }          });          window.aplayers || (window.aplayers = []);          window.aplayers.push(ap);        </script><p>当开启 Hexo 的 文章资源文件夹 功能时，可以将图片、音乐文件、歌词文件放入与文章对应的资源文件夹中，然后直接引用：</p><p>npm uninstall hexo-renderer-marked<br>npm install hexo-renderer-pandoc</p><div class="group-picture"><div class="group-picture-row"><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/FirstUrlBlog/1.png" class="" width="233"></div><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/FirstUrlBlog/1.png" class="" width="233"></div></div><div class="group-picture-row"><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/FirstUrlBlog/1.png" class="" width="233"></div><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/FirstUrlBlog/1.png" class="" width="233"></div><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/FirstUrlBlog/1.png" class="" width="233"></div></div></div><p>前面<img src="/FirstUrlBlog/1.png" class="" width="233">这个图片<br><img src="1.PNG" alt=""></p><!--![](FirstUrlBlog/1.PNG)  这个写法是从网页里找--><p>npm uninstall hexo-renderer-marked<br>npm install hexo-renderer-pandoc</p><p><a href="https://tding.top/archives/7e5b094d.html">https://tding.top/archives/7e5b094d.html</a> 性能优化<br><a href="https://ed521.github.io/2020/11/hexo-aplayer/">https://ed521.github.io/2020/11/hexo-aplayer/</a> 音乐<br><a href="https://easyliu-ly.github.io/2020/11/22/hexo/insert_video/">https://easyliu-ly.github.io/2020/11/22/hexo/insert_video/</a>  video</p>]]></content>
    
    
